{"tha-ap293:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap293:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap293:0.3":"Citakapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap293:1.1":"“Ajito nama namena, ","tha-ap293:1.2":"ahosim brahmano tada; ","tha-ap293:1.3":"Ahutim yitthukamoham, ","tha-ap293:1.4":"nanapuppham samanayim. ","tha-ap293:2.1":"Jalantam citakam disva, ","tha-ap293:2.2":"sikhino lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap293:2.3":"Tanca puppham samanetva, ","tha-ap293:2.4":"citake okirim aham. ","tha-ap293:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap293:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap293:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap293:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap293:4.1":"Sattavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap293:4.2":"sattasum manujadhipa; ","tha-ap293:4.3":"Supajjalitanama te, ","tha-ap293:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap293:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap293:5.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap293:5.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap293:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap293:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma citakapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap293:7.1":"Citakapujakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}